{"id": "1410007710669340802", "channel_id": "1409879666281418845", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "Lineup seems fine atp tho I recon you run Greed, Frenzy and Emerge as support wheels. Even tho they are of the lowest rarity, these are op for a ton of early content, also idk if you wanna run \"To my dearest friend\" on Caecus since he is the main dps since it gives crit rate to allies and not to him. The same goes for the other wheel, even tho Caecus makes use of existing counter stacks, he does not generate ones himself (Sure his Rouse generates 3 counter but that just isnt worth a whole wheel slot). Would make more sense to take the 2nd wheel from Hameln since it gives crit rate. But yeah, please read through the unit's skills and give them wheels based on that instead of putting on seemingly random stuff", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T21:07:14.900000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-26T21:11:46.184000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409879666281418845", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Just started", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1409778557412184064", "channel_id": "1409778557412184064", "type": 0, "author_id": "495110731620941825", "author_name": "amethystcat1975", "author_bot": false, "content": "How many dupes should I get of each for them to work well? Also does Hameln need his wheel or dupes more? I've been playing for about 2 weeks now and am mostly f2p and would appreciate the help. Thx!", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T05:56:40.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409778557412184064", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Dupes of Hameln, Horla, Corpo", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1409789595834515506", "channel_id": "1409778557412184064", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "Horla is great even at e0 so you can stop pulling for her dupes \n\nFor both Hameln and Corpo, you can go for e2 (2 dupes) if you can\nBoth are still good at e0 although they get great upgrades \n\nHameln e2 reduces the arith cost of the chosen card for his exalt by 2\n\nCorpo e1 gives more aliemus while her e2 adds weakness to her skill 2 and increases shield, strength gain, and tentacle dmg from her pilot", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T06:40:32.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-26T12:54:05.854000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409778557412184064", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Dupes of Hameln, Horla, Corpo", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
